---
title: Spicy Beef Tostadas with Guacamole and Cheese
description: Tostadas are simply toasted tortillas. It makes them deliciously crispy! We've given you more tortillas here than you need for the recipe and we hate the thought of them going to waste. Why not make your own tortilla chips with what's left? Just cut them into triangles, drizzle with oil and season with salt, black pepper and any other spices you fancy before baking in the oven until crunchy. Enjoy!
